Dear [@bill_first_name@],
[%content_zone id:'email_tracking_header'%][%end content_zone%]  
<p>
Thank you for shopping with [@send_from_company@].
</p>
<p>
Below is a list of items that have been Pack. A tax invoice has also been attached 
to this email for your records.
</p>
<p>
[%data id:'username' if:'ne' value:''%]
To track the progress of this and other orders online please go to <a href="[%URL page:'account'%][%END URL%]">your account</a> and select the order you want to track.
[%END data%]

[%data id:'username' if:'eq' value:''%]
To track the progress of your order online please <a href="[%URL page:'account' type:'nr_track_order' id:'[@order_id@]' qs:'email=[@email@]&zip=[@ship_zip@]'%][%END URL%]">click here.</a>
[%END data%]
</p>
